---
title: Shawarma-Inspired Chorizo Wraps with Crispy Shallots and Garlic Sauce
description: Chorizo sausage is seared with our Shawarma Spice Blend for a meal full of sweet and smoky aromas!  We've got crunchy and tart pickled cabbage as well as a bright herb and garlic sauce, all that's left to say is YUM YUM!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/wraps-de-chorizo-facon-shawarma-e0d514b5.jpg
